headline: Baxter Declares Quarterly Dividend
summary: DEERFIELD, Ill., November 11, 2025--Baxter International Inc. (NYSE:BAX), a global medtech leader, today announced that its Board of Directors has declared a quarterly cash dividend of $0.01 per share of common stock. The dividend is payable on Jan. 2, 2026, to stockholders of record as of Nov. 28, 2025. The indicated annual dividend rate equates to $0.04 per share of common stock.
